metadata.name: Mycoterra
metadata.description: Welcome to the world of Mycoterra, a universe filled with unique and colorful extraterrestrial creatures. Each token in this collection represents one of our hand-crafted alien beings, with their own distinct personality and attributes. These tokens are one-of-a-kind and available in a limited edition, making them a rare and valuable addition to any collection. Own a piece of Mycoterra today!
